{"word":"Hananiah","slug":"hananiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hananiah</b> <a href=\"#/H2608\">H2608</a> <br/> 1. Son of Heman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=4'>1Ch 25:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=23'>1Ch 25:23</a><br/> 2. A captain of Uzziah's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=11'>2Ch 26:11</a><br/> 3. Father of Zedekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=12'>Jer 36:12</a><br/> 4. A prophet of Gibeon who uttered false prophecies in the temple during the reign of Zedekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=28'>Jer 28</a><br/> 5. Grandfather of Irijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=13'>Jer 37:13</a><br/> 6. Son of Shashak<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=24'>1Ch 8:24</a><br/> 7. Hebrew name of Shadrach<br/> <a href='S:Shadrach'>Shadrach</a><br/> 8. Son of Zerubbabel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=19'>1Ch 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=21'>1Ch 3:21</a><br/> 9. Son of Bebai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=28'>Ezr 10:28</a><br/> 10. An apothecary and priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=8'>Neh 3:8</a><br/> 11. Son of Shelemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=30'>Neh 3:30</a><br/> 12. A keeper of the gates of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=2'>Neh 7:2</a><br/> 13. One who sealed the covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=23'>Neh 10:23</a><br/> 14. A priest in the time of Jehoiakim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=12'>Neh 12:12</a>; <a hr